WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.168 --> 01:43.954
=Episode 11=

01:45.757 --> 01:46.356
Mr. Zhou,

01:46.757 --> 01:48.397
my mother mentioned that you're

01:48.837 --> 01:49.757
in new medical tech.

01:50.076 --> 01:51.516
Ms. Ma invested in you.

01:52.397 --> 01:53.477
You're so busy every day.

01:53.557 --> 01:55.117
I'm so grateful that you still remember

01:55.236 --> 01:56.076
who I am.

01:56.637 --> 01:58.156
Thanks to Xu Yan for the introduction.

01:58.837 --> 01:59.316
Xu Yan.

01:59.917 --> 02:00.557
Toast you.

02:01.236 --> 02:01.956
I have to drive.

02:02.316 --> 02:02.837
Alright.

02:05.117 --> 02:05.997
Let's eat.

02:11.277 --> 02:12.316
How long have you met?

02:13.876 --> 02:14.277
We...

02:14.316 --> 02:15.077
Xu Yan and I

02:15.156 --> 02:16.196
have quite some history.

02:16.624 --> 02:19.476
We met when we first came to Jingzhou
to start our business.

02:22.756 --> 02:23.636
So it's been long.

02:24.077 --> 02:24.636
Right.

02:25.716 --> 02:26.837
But over these years,

02:26.916 --> 02:27.797
we've all been busy

02:27.876 --> 02:29.036
in our own fields.

02:29.277 --> 02:29.957
So

02:30.196 --> 02:31.237
we hardly met.

02:31.237 --> 02:33.232
True, we hardly met,

02:33.616 --> 02:34.916
but we've stayed in contact.

02:35.436 --> 02:37.237
Moreover, I'm very close to her family.

02:37.677 --> 02:39.557
I often chat with her parents

02:39.756 --> 02:40.636
by overseas calls.

02:43.957 --> 02:44.557
That close?

02:45.237 --> 02:46.357
You should meet more often.

02:47.436 --> 02:48.517
It's my fault.

02:48.756 --> 02:49.557
Over these years,

02:49.756 --> 02:51.596
I've thrown myself into work

02:53.036 --> 02:54.117
and drifted apart

02:54.117 --> 02:55.756
from my friends.

02:57.077 --> 02:58.476
Asking Xu Yan for help

02:58.557 --> 02:59.316
this time we met.

02:59.316 --> 03:00.557
Sorry about that.

03:02.677 --> 03:03.196
Mr. Shen.

03:03.677 --> 03:04.876
She knows me well.

03:05.036 --> 03:06.677
I'm direct.

03:07.316 --> 03:08.876
I asked her to contact you

03:08.916 --> 03:11.196
for your help with my company.

03:12.517 --> 03:13.077
Haoming.

03:14.517 --> 03:15.277
There's something

03:15.357 --> 03:16.476
I haven't told you.

03:17.196 --> 03:18.636
Zeyuan's company

03:19.156 --> 03:20.636
is in medical tech.

03:21.117 --> 03:22.316
I think Jinda Group

03:22.436 --> 03:24.237
lacks sufficient expertise
in medical fields.

03:24.596 --> 03:25.196
This time...

03:25.196 --> 03:26.156
I get it.

03:27.397 --> 03:29.196
I had similar concerns before.

03:29.596 --> 03:30.316
A few days ago,

03:30.316 --> 03:31.916
I had a chat with Mr. Xu on the phone.

03:32.557 --> 03:33.316
He said

03:33.316 --> 03:35.237
that every industry is embracing

03:35.237 --> 03:36.077
new technologies now.

03:36.237 --> 03:38.077
He strongly advised me to meet Mr. Shen

03:38.196 --> 03:38.837
and have a talk.

03:41.357 --> 03:42.916
Our group invests widely.

03:44.077 --> 03:45.036
If it's a good project,

03:45.436 --> 03:46.117
we're open.

03:46.277 --> 03:46.997
Great.

03:48.677 --> 03:49.517
Well,

03:49.997 --> 03:51.716
Mr. Xu has become an authority

03:52.077 --> 03:53.156
in construction

03:53.277 --> 03:54.476
after years of dedication.

03:54.876 --> 03:56.077
But he remains

03:56.077 --> 03:56.957
attentive to sectors

03:56.957 --> 03:58.196
like high-tech.

03:58.517 --> 04:00.036
That open mind

04:00.196 --> 04:01.277
is truly admirable.

04:01.397 --> 04:02.436
It's my fault.

04:02.957 --> 04:04.077
I don't communicate enough

04:04.237 --> 04:04.997
with my in-laws.

04:05.316 --> 04:06.316
I'll work on it.

04:07.316 --> 04:08.277
Strive to do better.

04:08.517 --> 04:08.876
Cheers.

04:10.237 --> 04:10.916
Don't just talk.

04:11.156 --> 04:11.636
Let's eat.

04:13.237 --> 04:14.036
Enjoy your meal.

04:14.237 --> 04:15.237
I'll step out.

04:15.876 --> 04:16.357
Take care.

04:17.196 --> 04:17.797
Enjoy.

04:20.477 --> 04:20.917
Mr. Shen.

04:21.396 --> 04:22.316
I'll briefly introduce

04:22.316 --> 04:23.076
my projects.

04:23.117 --> 04:23.717
Eat first.

04:26.396 --> 04:26.797
Okay.

05:24.997 --> 05:26.557
Your behavior surprised me.

05:27.276 --> 05:28.956
I thought we've reached a consensus.

05:28.956 --> 05:31.117
We were on the same side.

05:31.316 --> 05:33.157
We never were.

05:35.557 --> 05:37.836
That's harsh.

05:38.157 --> 05:40.597
I've been covering for you.

05:40.876 --> 05:41.797
And you repay me

05:41.836 --> 05:43.357
by blocking me?

05:51.357 --> 05:52.917
Did I speak too much just now?

05:52.917 --> 05:54.436
Did I cause you any trouble?

05:54.836 --> 05:55.717
Would your husband

05:56.037 --> 05:57.076
suddenly get the urge

05:57.396 --> 05:59.076
to call his father-in-law overseas

05:59.076 --> 05:59.997
on a whim?

06:11.677 --> 06:13.237
If you keep resisting me,

06:14.717 --> 06:15.797
I really can't guarantee

06:15.836 --> 06:17.196
what I'll say next.

06:19.636 --> 06:21.037
No matter what you'll say,

06:22.076 --> 06:23.597
I won't let Shen Haoming

06:23.756 --> 06:25.316
get dragged into your scam.

06:26.117 --> 06:27.597
Worst case, we both go down.

06:28.836 --> 06:30.117
I'll face the consequences,

06:30.917 --> 06:31.756
you too.

06:32.117 --> 06:33.396
You've got everything you want.

06:35.396 --> 06:36.436
Can you discard them?

06:38.157 --> 06:39.276
You're bluffing.

06:39.756 --> 06:41.357
You're scared, actually.

06:41.477 --> 06:42.636
You know very well

06:42.797 --> 06:44.836
you'll lose the most in the end.

06:45.677 --> 06:46.677
What do I have to fear?

06:46.997 --> 06:48.876
I have nothing to lose.

06:48.917 --> 06:49.717
I have no fear!

06:49.756 --> 06:50.557
Good.

06:51.396 --> 06:53.037
Then go tell Shen Haoming

06:53.117 --> 06:54.836
the whole truth right now.

07:01.717 --> 07:02.797
Seems you're really

07:02.797 --> 07:04.237
trying to be his perfect wife.

07:06.076 --> 07:06.797
Fine.

07:07.956 --> 07:10.037
Don't want to use his money?

07:12.876 --> 07:13.477
Give yours

07:15.117 --> 07:15.997
to me.

07:19.396 --> 07:21.276
You have one night to think.

07:21.876 --> 07:23.797
Or I'll expose you online.

07:34.076 --> 07:35.157
A friendly reminder to you.

07:37.276 --> 07:39.237
A man drowning in debt

07:43.237 --> 07:44.396
is a devil.

08:25.276 --> 08:26.557
Remember to pay up.

08:27.076 --> 08:27.597
Otherwise,

08:27.597 --> 08:29.557
I'll haunt you like one.

08:35.477 --> 08:37.156
What are you doing?

08:49.477 --> 08:50.556
(Zhou Zeyuan)
Look into this guy for me.

08:53.077 --> 08:53.636
Okay.

09:00.837 --> 09:02.117
I've told you.

09:03.437 --> 09:04.717
I won't help you.

09:05.916 --> 09:07.437
Solve your own mess.

09:08.117 --> 09:08.676
And

09:09.516 --> 09:10.036
don't

09:10.036 --> 09:11.036
call me again.

09:13.237 --> 09:13.796
Yan.

09:19.077 --> 09:21.276
Who's that?

09:23.197 --> 09:24.077
Work call.

09:25.957 --> 09:26.597
What's wrong?

09:26.876 --> 09:27.556
Did I awake you?

09:28.636 --> 09:29.237
It's nothing.

09:31.040 --> 09:32.876
(New message received)

09:32.876 --> 09:34.237
If it's work-related,

09:34.717 --> 09:36.156
is there anything I can help with?

09:37.317 --> 09:38.156
No.

09:38.477 --> 09:39.636
They just informed me

09:40.156 --> 09:41.117
tomorrow's guests

09:41.197 --> 09:42.477
may cancel

09:42.957 --> 09:43.997
due to weather.

09:44.237 --> 09:45.437
I told them

09:46.036 --> 09:47.717
to handle it on their own.

09:50.676 --> 09:52.437
You seem tired lately.

09:52.837 --> 09:54.096
Don't push yourself too hard.

09:59.276 --> 10:00.357
A little, indeed.

10:01.597 --> 10:02.796
I have

10:02.837 --> 10:03.837
two shows at once.

10:05.036 --> 10:06.516
And I just started anchoring.

10:07.276 --> 10:08.396
It's exhausting.

10:10.077 --> 10:11.357
If it's too much,

10:12.117 --> 10:12.756
just

10:13.516 --> 10:14.197
drop one.

10:16.636 --> 10:17.636
But you know

10:17.636 --> 10:19.477
being a news anchor is my dream.

10:21.077 --> 10:23.117
And I built Family Feast from scratch.

10:24.876 --> 10:26.036
I can't give up either.

10:27.036 --> 10:27.796
Then I support you.

10:28.477 --> 10:29.556
Keep both.

10:32.276 --> 10:33.357
You changed so fast.

10:34.756 --> 10:36.796
(Zhou Zeyuan)
I'll always choose your choice.

10:37.276 --> 10:40.036
(Xu Yan, think about the consequences
of refusing me.)

10:50.563 --> 10:51.376
(Phone off)

10:56.676 --> 10:58.276
Having someone supporting me

10:59.717 --> 11:00.357
feels good.

11:01.916 --> 11:03.197
I stand by what I said.

11:03.717 --> 11:05.197
Do whatever you want.

11:06.197 --> 11:07.357
Mistakes don't matter.

11:08.237 --> 11:08.997
Even if you fail,

11:09.636 --> 11:10.957
we can start over.

11:21.876 --> 11:22.636
Sorry.

11:22.876 --> 11:24.837
The number you dialed is powered off.

11:30.256 --> 11:32.624
(Xu Yan)

11:57.276 --> 11:57.997
No answer.

11:58.237 --> 11:59.237
No reply.

11:59.676 --> 12:00.437
Xu Yan.

12:00.636 --> 12:01.796
What are you thinking?

12:01.997 --> 12:03.156
I've got nothing to say.

12:03.556 --> 12:04.717
My cash flow's gone,

12:04.796 --> 12:05.516
salaries unpaid,

12:05.597 --> 12:06.997
investors digging into my books.

12:07.156 --> 12:08.477
My company's about to collapse.

12:08.477 --> 12:09.636
I'm cornered.

12:09.756 --> 12:10.477
I'm telling you.

12:10.796 --> 12:11.837
If I go down,

12:11.957 --> 12:12.916
I'm dragging you.

12:12.997 --> 12:13.957
Understood?

12:15.077 --> 12:16.117
Let go of me!

12:16.597 --> 12:17.904
- Let go!
- What are you doing?

12:18.477 --> 12:19.837
What are you doing?

12:21.156 --> 12:21.837
Who are you?

12:21.957 --> 12:23.197
Who are you?

12:23.197 --> 12:24.117
None of your business.

12:24.117 --> 12:24.876
Don't step in.

12:24.876 --> 12:25.317
Go away!

12:26.437 --> 12:26.916
Listen up.

12:26.997 --> 12:27.837
There are many

12:27.916 --> 12:28.437
cameras here.

12:28.437 --> 12:29.237
All recording.

12:29.357 --> 12:30.224
I'll call the police!

12:30.477 --> 12:31.276
Right now.

12:35.756 --> 12:36.156
Hello?

12:36.437 --> 12:37.077
Police?

12:37.396 --> 12:38.317
Someone's harassing me!

12:38.516 --> 12:39.197
Guards!

12:39.516 --> 12:40.197
Help!

12:52.357 --> 12:53.296
Drink something warm.

12:53.997 --> 12:54.357
Thanks.

13:00.276 --> 13:00.717
Yan.

13:01.556 --> 13:02.957
Who was that guy?

13:03.036 --> 13:04.437
What's going on?

13:07.957 --> 13:08.916
Just someone I knew.

13:08.997 --> 13:09.997
We had a small dispute.

13:10.556 --> 13:11.636
But it's all settled now.

13:11.676 --> 13:12.437
Don't worry.

13:14.396 --> 13:16.516
He looked menacing.

13:16.597 --> 13:18.477
Didn't seem a small matter.

13:22.957 --> 13:24.117
You are still the same.

13:24.676 --> 13:26.156
Keeping everything bottled up.

13:26.997 --> 13:28.077
Truly, I may not

13:28.197 --> 13:28.876
be much help

13:28.957 --> 13:30.197
if you tell me.

13:34.756 --> 13:36.156
You're still the same too,

13:37.477 --> 13:38.676
hot-tempered.

13:39.876 --> 13:40.676
Thank you.

13:42.357 --> 13:43.676
I should be thanking you.

13:44.317 --> 13:45.756
Yu Yiming told me everything.

13:46.756 --> 13:49.997
You paid my adult education tuition

13:49.997 --> 13:51.276
for next semester.

13:52.276 --> 13:52.837
Why?

13:53.357 --> 13:54.317
Why hide it?

13:55.077 --> 13:55.957
Trying to be a saint?

13:56.036 --> 13:57.117
Do good deeds anonymously?

13:57.437 --> 13:58.556
It's nothing.

14:01.717 --> 14:03.156
So today you came to see me?

14:06.876 --> 14:08.117
To give you this.

14:09.357 --> 14:11.516
Some makeup,

14:11.997 --> 14:13.676
just to thank you.

14:16.117 --> 14:17.437
I was waiting

14:17.477 --> 14:18.396
at the main entrance.

14:18.597 --> 14:20.317
But you drove straight to the basement,

14:20.317 --> 14:21.117
didn't notice me.

14:21.197 --> 14:22.077
So I went

14:22.077 --> 14:23.317
down to find you.

14:24.876 --> 14:25.197
And...

14:25.556 --> 14:26.317
About

14:26.437 --> 14:27.997
Lin Tao's matter,

14:28.876 --> 14:30.237
I was too harsh.

14:30.237 --> 14:31.516
I wanted to apologize.

14:32.077 --> 14:33.036
I'm sorry, Yan.

14:38.957 --> 14:40.756
I was impulsive too.

14:43.036 --> 14:43.756
I'm sorry.

14:45.516 --> 14:46.796
I like the gift. Thanks.

14:46.997 --> 14:47.796
I'll keep it.

14:53.676 --> 14:55.876
Has his bothered you again?

14:56.796 --> 14:57.396
No.

14:57.916 --> 14:58.597
Good.

14:59.876 --> 15:00.957
I can't help you much.

15:01.117 --> 15:02.156
But Yan,

15:02.317 --> 15:03.317
as long as I'm here,

15:03.837 --> 15:05.276
nobody's bullying you.

15:05.756 --> 15:06.480
I'll protect you.

15:09.117 --> 15:10.036
So today,

15:10.516 --> 15:11.276
your treat.

15:12.276 --> 15:13.437
I already paid.

15:16.957 --> 15:17.904
That's not your style.

15:18.676 --> 15:19.317
Hello.

15:21.317 --> 15:22.516
Your most expensive cake,

15:22.597 --> 15:23.396
please.

15:23.437 --> 15:23.837
Thanks.

15:23.837 --> 15:24.624
- One moment.
- Thank you.

15:25.197 --> 15:26.036
Thank you.

15:27.756 --> 15:28.516
Your treat.

15:31.796 --> 15:32.317
Yan.

15:32.477 --> 15:33.876
Here's the news file.

15:33.957 --> 15:34.516
Thanks.

15:37.156 --> 15:37.756
Dong Chao.

15:39.357 --> 15:40.077
Close the door.

15:45.207 --> 15:52.112
(Incoming call from Qiao Jianbin)

15:55.756 --> 15:56.276
What's wrong?

15:56.556 --> 15:57.036
Qiao Yan.

15:57.597 --> 15:58.916
Your mom and I are in Jingzhou.

15:59.197 --> 16:00.437
Sending you the hotel address.

16:00.876 --> 16:02.117
Come right now.

16:02.437 --> 16:04.357
Don't ask. We'll talk in person.

16:08.976 --> 16:10.800
(From Qiao Jianbin
Wuseshi Hotel)

16:24.997 --> 16:26.197
Why are you here?

16:26.957 --> 16:27.916
Come in.

16:31.876 --> 16:32.717
You've arrived.

17:10.197 --> 17:11.637
I invited your parents here.

17:13.316 --> 17:13.957
Qiao Yan.

17:14.917 --> 17:16.637
No one loves us more

17:17.157 --> 17:18.637
than our parents.

17:19.836 --> 17:20.877
As children,

17:21.316 --> 17:22.356
we shouldn't hide anything

17:22.717 --> 17:23.917
from them.

17:25.316 --> 17:26.957
Maybe you've had

17:27.116 --> 17:28.237
some conflicts.

17:28.796 --> 17:29.516
But I believe

17:29.877 --> 17:31.116
if you sit down

17:31.397 --> 17:32.237
and talk openly

17:32.477 --> 17:33.756
with each other,

17:34.276 --> 17:34.836
everything

17:34.997 --> 17:36.437
will be resolved.

17:37.197 --> 17:37.877
Right, Mr. Qiao?

17:41.276 --> 17:42.917
Qiao Yan is a good girl.

17:43.677 --> 17:45.276
Don't be too angry.

17:45.316 --> 17:46.036
Take care.

17:46.516 --> 17:47.836
I've arranged the rooms.

17:48.036 --> 17:49.316
Stay as long as you want.

17:49.516 --> 17:50.477
Then I'll head back.

17:50.796 --> 17:51.356
Okay.

17:51.957 --> 17:52.877
I'm leaving.

18:16.237 --> 18:17.836
Where did you get the nerve

18:19.356 --> 18:20.836
to fake your parents' jobs

18:21.197 --> 18:23.516
and hire actors at your wedding?

18:23.917 --> 18:24.917
Who gave you the courage

18:25.036 --> 18:26.997
to tell such a lie?

18:27.437 --> 18:28.717
I, Qiao Jianbin,

18:28.836 --> 18:29.756
have never done

18:29.836 --> 18:31.397
a shameful thing in my life.

18:31.756 --> 18:33.677
How did I raise a daughter like you?

18:33.877 --> 18:34.677
Calm down.

18:37.437 --> 18:38.157
Yan.

18:38.957 --> 18:40.556
Just tell your father the truth.

18:40.677 --> 18:41.877
Why did you do this?

18:42.157 --> 18:43.116
Why?

18:43.877 --> 18:46.116
Greedy for wealth
and blinded by ambition.

18:46.516 --> 18:47.596
To marry into riches,

18:47.677 --> 18:49.516
you've abandoned all moral principles!

18:52.516 --> 18:54.437
I didn't take a single penny
from the Shens.

18:55.556 --> 18:57.356
My feelings for Shen Haoming are real.

18:58.356 --> 18:59.076
I love him,

18:59.397 --> 19:00.477
so I want to marry him

19:00.516 --> 19:01.677
and become his wife.

19:03.157 --> 19:04.157
I did nothing wrong

19:05.157 --> 19:05.877
with that.

19:06.356 --> 19:07.796
Ridiculous!

19:08.116 --> 19:09.556
You fooled everyone.

19:10.076 --> 19:11.917
You played us all!

19:12.197 --> 19:12.957
You think that

19:12.997 --> 19:14.397
will erase everything?

19:14.437 --> 19:15.437
Who would believe that?

19:15.637 --> 19:16.596
I don't need you to.

19:18.677 --> 19:19.516
I never

19:19.516 --> 19:20.356
expected

19:20.437 --> 19:21.836
you to understand me.

19:22.276 --> 19:23.316
I just want to say.

19:23.596 --> 19:24.957
No matter when

19:25.356 --> 19:26.796
I met someone like Shen Haoming,

19:26.836 --> 19:27.756
I would use

19:28.356 --> 19:29.677
any means

19:30.717 --> 19:31.796
necessary

19:32.556 --> 19:33.437
to be with him.

19:33.717 --> 19:35.237
But you shouldn't have deceived him!

19:35.237 --> 19:36.957
I didn't want to.

19:39.356 --> 19:40.917
It's just that since I was little,

19:41.637 --> 19:43.677
I knew I could only rely on myself.

19:49.917 --> 19:50.437
Yan.

19:51.877 --> 19:52.957
When you were a kid,

19:52.997 --> 19:54.316
we didn't raise you.

19:55.516 --> 19:57.957
But we took you back later.

19:58.836 --> 20:00.997
We've raised you all these years.

20:01.596 --> 20:03.157
You can't blame your mistakes

20:03.237 --> 20:04.917
all on us!

20:09.596 --> 20:10.157
No.

20:17.836 --> 20:19.796
You'll not understand
what you did wrong.

20:20.556 --> 20:21.836
My only mistake

20:22.556 --> 20:24.197
was not exposing you earlier!

20:25.076 --> 20:26.756
I'll go confront the Shen family now

20:26.917 --> 20:28.076
and expose everything!

20:28.197 --> 20:28.917
Qiao! Qiao!

20:29.036 --> 20:29.756
Don't go! Don't!

20:29.877 --> 20:30.556
Calm down!

20:30.717 --> 20:31.477
Let go!

20:31.717 --> 20:32.756
Think about Yan!

20:32.836 --> 20:34.437
If you do this, her career is ruined!

20:34.596 --> 20:36.076
If I didn't know, fine.

20:36.197 --> 20:37.596
But now, if I cover for her,

20:37.717 --> 20:38.997
I'd be failing as a father!

20:38.997 --> 20:40.437
She's already married.

20:40.477 --> 20:41.516
You can't do this.

20:41.596 --> 20:42.756
What's this act about?

20:49.596 --> 20:49.997
Well.

20:51.556 --> 20:52.276
What are you

20:53.717 --> 20:54.957
acting out here?

20:56.116 --> 20:56.836
Parents

20:57.116 --> 20:58.157
brokenhearted

20:58.157 --> 21:00.397
over their daughter's mistakes?

21:05.356 --> 21:06.477
Do you really care?

21:09.957 --> 21:11.596
This is how I grew up.

21:11.637 --> 21:12.877
You never cared about me!

21:13.397 --> 21:14.917
I fought so hard

21:14.957 --> 21:16.157
to get where I am today,

21:17.397 --> 21:18.717
to get a loving husband.

21:21.157 --> 21:22.116
Are you unhappy?

21:27.157 --> 21:27.877
I got it.

21:29.157 --> 21:30.157
You think

21:30.197 --> 21:30.957
this life

21:30.957 --> 21:32.637
should've belonged to Qiao Lin,

21:32.637 --> 21:33.276
not me, right?

21:36.237 --> 21:37.036
Or you want

21:37.036 --> 21:38.637
to expose me to the Shen family

21:38.756 --> 21:39.316
so you can

21:39.316 --> 21:40.677
extort money from me?

21:42.516 --> 21:43.836
Fine. No problem.

21:44.076 --> 21:45.237
I'll pay.

21:46.076 --> 21:46.864
What did you say?

21:48.756 --> 21:50.677
How could you think that?

21:52.437 --> 21:53.116
You...

21:54.756 --> 21:56.756
Are you still

21:56.796 --> 21:57.957
a Qiao family's girl?

21:58.356 --> 21:59.756
Do you still bear our surname?

21:59.917 --> 22:01.036
I don't bear Qiao.

22:04.677 --> 22:05.877
My name is Xu Yan.

22:07.237 --> 22:07.836
Good.

22:10.397 --> 22:13.036
From now on,
we're no longer father and daughter.

22:14.356 --> 22:16.397
You are not part of this family anymore!

22:16.437 --> 22:16.957
No!

22:17.997 --> 22:18.637
Qiao!

23:19.824 --> 23:22.416
(Secretary Chen)

23:23.237 --> 23:24.076
- Go ahead.
- Mr. Shen.

23:24.437 --> 23:25.237
Your wife

23:25.276 --> 23:26.556
sold the car

23:27.397 --> 23:28.116
you gifted her.

23:32.836 --> 23:33.477
Got it.

23:42.637 --> 23:44.116
I've given you the money.

23:47.076 --> 23:48.197
What do you want?

23:52.076 --> 23:53.637
Are you throwing scraps on me?

23:54.116 --> 23:55.116
Do you know how much

23:55.116 --> 23:56.596
my company spends every day?

23:58.756 --> 24:00.116
Zhou Zeyuan, I'm warning you.

24:00.397 --> 24:01.556
This is the first

24:02.477 --> 24:03.596
and the last time.

24:05.756 --> 24:06.756
Take this money

24:06.756 --> 24:07.637
as your hush fee,

24:07.717 --> 24:08.596
for your last life.

24:08.917 --> 24:09.997
I won't tolerate

24:10.276 --> 24:11.877
endless extortion.

24:16.637 --> 24:17.637
Try this again,

24:22.237 --> 24:23.556
and I'll call the police.

24:25.556 --> 24:26.997
But the deficit's too large.

24:27.237 --> 24:28.877
This is far from enough.

24:31.997 --> 24:33.596
If my company crashes,

24:33.796 --> 24:35.356
everyone will come

24:35.397 --> 24:36.477
demanding repayment.

24:36.836 --> 24:38.877
Then it'll be do-or-die.

24:42.677 --> 24:44.397
But the one who should be afraid

24:44.397 --> 24:45.316
isn't me.

24:45.756 --> 24:46.437
It's you.

24:47.276 --> 24:49.276
Everything you schemed so hard to get

24:49.276 --> 24:50.556
will turn to ashes.

24:51.836 --> 24:52.556
Xu Yan.

24:53.437 --> 24:55.356
Do you dare gamble everything?

24:55.717 --> 24:56.637
Can't you see

24:56.717 --> 24:57.756
I've been

24:57.836 --> 24:58.957
giving you chances?

25:00.836 --> 25:01.316
Fine.

25:06.756 --> 25:07.556
Give it a try then.

25:09.877 --> 25:11.157
See who can go further.

25:20.316 --> 25:21.477
If I end up in jail,

25:21.917 --> 25:23.796
- at least I'll have you with me.
- Let go!

25:37.197 --> 25:38.356
Ten million per blow.

25:40.596 --> 25:41.637
Another strike?

25:44.976 --> 25:46.416
(Mr. Shen)

25:47.677 --> 25:48.796
Your husband's calling.

25:55.504 --> 25:56.720
(Mr. Shen)

25:59.024 --> 25:59.984
(Mr. Shen)

26:01.116 --> 26:02.076
Hello, Mr. Shen.

26:02.237 --> 26:03.237
What's up?

26:03.756 --> 26:04.677
2 PM.

26:05.237 --> 26:06.157
Golf game.

26:06.276 --> 26:06.836
Available?

26:07.397 --> 26:08.796
Of course.

26:11.276 --> 26:12.637
He walked into this himself.

26:12.717 --> 26:13.516
Not my fault.

26:19.477 --> 26:20.397
Listen well.

26:21.877 --> 26:23.276
If you hurt him,

26:24.076 --> 26:24.997
I won't let you go.

26:26.836 --> 26:28.316
You want to expose me?

26:29.197 --> 26:29.877
Go ahead!

26:39.036 --> 26:39.917
Mr. Shen.

26:40.677 --> 26:42.637
Sorry, I forgot to tell you.

26:43.237 --> 26:44.877
Xu Yan is with me now.

26:45.516 --> 26:46.877
She says she's coming too.

26:48.157 --> 26:48.836
Got it.

26:49.756 --> 26:50.437
Goodbye.

26:56.237 --> 26:56.997
To put it simply,

26:57.116 --> 26:58.036
the idea is to combine

26:58.036 --> 26:59.157
the thinking and experience

26:59.237 --> 27:00.516
of top medical experts

27:00.756 --> 27:01.957
with new technologies

27:02.036 --> 27:03.437
in each case.

27:03.877 --> 27:04.756
Then we can replicate

27:04.756 --> 27:06.556
countless top doctors

27:06.637 --> 27:07.516
to serve patients.

27:08.437 --> 27:09.677
Jinda Group hasn't touched

27:10.036 --> 27:11.677
the medical field yet.

27:12.276 --> 27:13.197
But I'm interested.

27:14.276 --> 27:15.237
What's the return rate?

27:16.917 --> 27:17.917
This round, we're raising

27:17.917 --> 27:18.877
100 million.

27:19.276 --> 27:20.036
I saved

27:20.076 --> 27:20.877
50 million for you.

27:21.237 --> 27:22.276
Based on current

27:22.316 --> 27:22.957
figures,

27:23.036 --> 27:23.877
the annualized return

27:23.917 --> 27:24.957
is around 20%.

27:25.197 --> 27:26.076
10 million a year.

27:26.316 --> 27:26.796
Of course,

27:26.917 --> 27:28.756
the more you put in,
the higher the returns.

27:38.796 --> 27:39.477
Nice shot.

27:40.076 --> 27:40.556
Your turn.

27:41.356 --> 27:41.756
Okay.

27:49.316 --> 27:50.556
Looks like

27:50.836 --> 27:52.197
you haven't been practicing.

27:53.637 --> 27:54.877
Can't compare with you.

27:55.677 --> 27:56.157
Mr. Shen.

27:56.556 --> 27:58.197
The project we discussed,

27:58.316 --> 27:59.677
I've been developing it for years.

28:00.477 --> 28:01.957
From medical R&D

28:02.116 --> 28:03.076
to data collection,

28:03.276 --> 28:04.437
our company leads

28:04.437 --> 28:05.796
in the industry.

28:06.356 --> 28:07.076
I believe,

28:07.356 --> 28:09.356
with your financial support,

28:09.477 --> 28:10.477
it'll take off.

28:10.796 --> 28:12.036
Not just substantial returns,

28:12.157 --> 28:13.076
but also solving

28:13.076 --> 28:14.276
real problems for patients.

28:14.397 --> 28:15.477
Good for the people.

28:15.836 --> 28:16.356
Okay.

28:16.957 --> 28:18.356
I've got the picture.

28:18.596 --> 28:20.157
I'll discuss it internally.

28:21.917 --> 28:22.957
Should be feasible.

28:23.197 --> 28:25.356
My secretary will update you.

28:26.836 --> 28:27.316
Okay.

28:27.957 --> 28:28.957
Thank you so much

28:29.076 --> 28:29.917
for this opportunity.

28:30.036 --> 28:30.556
No problem.

28:30.717 --> 28:31.516
I'll take my leave.

28:32.437 --> 28:32.836
Xu Yan.

28:33.157 --> 28:33.877
I'm heading out.

28:35.917 --> 28:36.276
Goodbye.

28:36.756 --> 28:37.157
Goodbye.

28:45.237 --> 28:45.677
What's up?

28:50.276 --> 28:50.836
Haoming.

28:51.796 --> 28:52.717
I don't think

28:52.717 --> 28:53.917
you should invest.

28:55.877 --> 28:56.717
First,

28:57.316 --> 28:58.237
we don't know much

28:58.276 --> 28:59.197
about medicine.

28:59.917 --> 29:00.516
Second,

29:01.356 --> 29:02.917
we don't know his company's

29:03.036 --> 29:03.756
operations either.

29:05.276 --> 29:06.717
It's too risky.

29:09.276 --> 29:10.877
Don't do it for my sake.

29:11.677 --> 29:12.556
I'm not

29:13.477 --> 29:14.637
that close to him.

29:15.316 --> 29:16.197
So,

29:16.917 --> 29:17.756
the investment...

29:18.237 --> 29:19.756
Actually,

29:20.637 --> 29:21.997
the funds he wants aren't huge.

29:22.756 --> 29:24.076
The medical field

29:24.316 --> 29:26.036
isn't our business,

29:26.917 --> 29:27.877
so I won't use

29:27.957 --> 29:28.756
Jinda's funds.

29:29.477 --> 29:31.276
I'll find other investors.

29:31.637 --> 29:32.437
It'll work out.

29:35.556 --> 29:37.116
With you handling it, of course.

29:40.237 --> 29:41.197
But 50 million

29:41.397 --> 29:42.437
isn't small.

29:42.596 --> 29:44.596
The risks and potential losses

29:45.116 --> 29:45.877
are

29:45.877 --> 29:47.036
within acceptable limits.

29:47.596 --> 29:48.356
I can handle it.

29:48.677 --> 29:49.397
Trust me.

29:51.316 --> 29:51.796
Let's go.

29:52.796 --> 29:53.477
Haoming.

29:57.756 --> 29:59.237
There's something I want to tell you.

29:59.316 --> 30:00.717
I want to tell you,

30:01.556 --> 30:03.157
I just want you by my side,

30:03.637 --> 30:05.276
happy

30:05.717 --> 30:06.717
and carefree.

30:08.516 --> 30:09.677
Not frowning.

30:11.836 --> 30:12.637
Smile.

30:17.836 --> 30:18.397
Let's go.

30:36.836 --> 30:37.477
Mr. Shen.

30:38.116 --> 30:39.437
Mr. Huang's secretary called,

30:39.920 --> 30:41.936
asking if you're available
the day after tomorrow.

30:42.197 --> 30:42.796
He will bring

30:42.796 --> 30:43.717
some important guests

30:43.796 --> 30:44.477
to play golf.

30:45.276 --> 30:45.796
No problem.

30:46.116 --> 30:46.477
And,

30:47.437 --> 30:48.917
Zhou Zeyuan's called multiple times.

30:49.036 --> 30:49.637
Looks like

30:49.917 --> 30:50.717
he's about to crack.

30:52.836 --> 30:53.397
No rush.

30:54.036 --> 30:54.796
Let him wait.

30:56.917 --> 30:59.596
Schedule a meeting with
the investment department in 15 minutes.

30:59.596 --> 31:00.116
Understood.

31:20.836 --> 31:21.356
Mr. Zhou.

31:21.997 --> 31:22.957
Our account funds

31:23.036 --> 31:24.116
can only sustain us

31:24.157 --> 31:24.997
for two days.

31:25.756 --> 31:27.076
Keep calling Shen Haoming.

31:27.917 --> 31:29.157
I've called numerous times.

31:29.397 --> 31:30.836
His secretary always makes excuses.

31:30.957 --> 31:32.197
Enough!

31:32.356 --> 31:34.197
Just call!

31:34.397 --> 31:35.197
Or tell me

31:35.356 --> 31:36.036
where else

31:36.076 --> 31:37.036
we can get money!

31:38.437 --> 31:39.157
Make the call!

31:53.677 --> 31:54.397
Secretary Chen.

31:54.796 --> 31:55.717
Congras, Mr. Zhou.

31:56.316 --> 31:57.076
Mr. Shen

31:57.157 --> 31:58.637
has agreed to invest.

31:59.237 --> 31:59.877
Moreover,

32:00.116 --> 32:01.717
he's willing to add more.

32:02.157 --> 32:02.836
However,

32:03.756 --> 32:04.997
he wants

32:04.997 --> 32:06.276
a 6% higher return.

32:06.877 --> 32:07.516
Is that okay?

32:08.157 --> 32:08.596
Sure.

32:08.717 --> 32:09.637
No problem at all.

32:10.796 --> 32:11.477
Secretary Chen,

32:11.877 --> 32:13.157
please inform Mr. Shen

32:13.397 --> 32:14.516
I'll make arrangements now.

32:14.877 --> 32:16.036
When he's not busy,

32:16.116 --> 32:17.796
I'll visit with the contract.

32:18.997 --> 32:19.957
There's no hurry.

32:20.677 --> 32:21.596
Mr. Shen

32:21.836 --> 32:22.677
thinks your sector

32:22.677 --> 32:24.076
is potential.

32:24.596 --> 32:25.116
However,

32:25.677 --> 32:26.997
it's his personal interest.

32:27.596 --> 32:28.116
The money

32:28.116 --> 32:29.157
won't be from

32:29.157 --> 32:29.796
Jinda Group.

32:30.316 --> 32:31.477
A professional agent will

32:31.997 --> 32:32.796
handle the contract.

32:33.237 --> 32:33.997
He'll contact you

32:33.997 --> 32:34.637
later.

32:35.356 --> 32:36.877
The funds will

32:37.796 --> 32:38.556
be transferred

32:39.036 --> 32:39.756
in batches

32:39.957 --> 32:40.796
within three months.

32:41.917 --> 32:42.516
Understood.

32:43.076 --> 32:44.276
Don't worry.

32:44.356 --> 32:44.917
I won't tell

32:44.957 --> 32:46.356
anyone about this.

32:46.877 --> 32:47.957
I'm grateful to him

32:48.036 --> 32:49.437
for recognizing my project

32:49.556 --> 32:51.036
and me.

32:51.717 --> 32:52.237
Okay.

32:53.076 --> 32:54.477
I'll convey

32:54.637 --> 32:55.917
your gratitude to him.

32:56.356 --> 32:56.836
Goodbye.

32:57.997 --> 32:58.836
Okay. Goodbye.

33:07.312 --> 33:08.688
(Four months later)

33:08.796 --> 33:09.356
Miss Xu.

33:09.836 --> 33:11.437
Nice job hosting the finance news.

33:11.917 --> 33:13.237
Since you've joined Family Feast,

33:13.477 --> 33:14.116
from today,

33:14.596 --> 33:16.717
take charge of that show too.

34:17.328 --> 34:18.192
(Zhou Zeyuan)

34:23.116 --> 34:24.437
(It suddenly dawned on me)

34:25.236 --> 34:27.156
(that it's been four months)

34:27.997 --> 34:30.156
(since Zhou Zeyuan last contacted me.)

34:33.156 --> 34:35.357
(He disappeared)

34:36.397 --> 34:37.516
(without a trace.)

34:50.357 --> 34:51.236
Is dinner ready?

34:52.156 --> 34:53.116
Yes. Go wash your hands.

34:54.116 --> 34:54.672
Smells great.

34:55.917 --> 34:56.596
Zhou Zeyuan's

34:56.917 --> 34:57.556
arrested.

35:02.116 --> 35:03.357
When?

35:03.596 --> 35:04.757
I just heard about it.

35:09.917 --> 35:10.437
(Recently,)

35:10.596 --> 35:12.556
(head of a well-known medical company,)

35:12.716 --> 35:13.397
(Zhou Zeyuan,)

35:13.716 --> 35:17.116
(has been arrested for financial fraud,)

35:17.196 --> 35:19.877
(collusion with foreign charities,
and illegally transferring)

35:19.877 --> 35:20.877
(investors' funds.)

35:20.877 --> 35:21.516
That's too much.

35:21.636 --> 35:23.196
(He was apprehended at a Macau casino,)

35:23.477 --> 35:24.397
(for investigation.)

35:35.437 --> 35:36.036
Honey.

35:37.196 --> 35:37.997
You've promised

35:37.997 --> 35:39.556
to invest in him.

35:40.156 --> 35:41.437
Will this affect you?

35:41.676 --> 35:42.516
No.

35:43.757 --> 35:46.917
I heard he was a gambling addict,

35:47.757 --> 35:49.296
so I ended the cooperation long ago.

35:49.797 --> 35:50.877
Moreover, my funds

35:50.877 --> 35:53.156
are managed by professional brokers.

35:53.757 --> 35:55.076
There shouldn't be any issues.

35:59.156 --> 35:59.797
That's great.

36:00.397 --> 36:01.317
But you...

36:02.676 --> 36:03.917
You sold your car, didn't you?

36:13.757 --> 36:15.397
Because I heard Ms. Ma

36:16.917 --> 36:18.236
also invested heavily in him.

36:19.716 --> 36:21.877
She doesn't care about returns.

36:25.116 --> 36:25.837
Why?

36:26.477 --> 36:27.397
As everyone knows,

36:28.317 --> 36:29.797
Ms. Ma's patronized

36:30.277 --> 36:31.196
many upstarts

36:32.236 --> 36:33.716
as Zhou Zeyuan.

36:34.076 --> 36:35.196
She enjoys being surrounded

36:35.357 --> 36:36.397
by those

36:37.236 --> 36:38.236
promising youths.

36:39.516 --> 36:40.556
You fell for her act.

36:45.437 --> 36:47.236
Actually, she knew all along

36:47.236 --> 36:48.277
what Zhou was really like.

36:56.236 --> 36:57.516
Try the shrimp.

36:58.156 --> 36:59.357
Last time you said it's salty.

36:59.636 --> 37:00.036
How's it?

37:01.596 --> 37:01.997
Better?

37:05.437 --> 37:06.397
Not salty at all.

37:11.957 --> 37:12.556
Yan.

37:14.716 --> 37:16.236
If you want to invest

37:16.636 --> 37:17.317
in the future,

37:18.196 --> 37:19.236
just ask me for money.

37:20.357 --> 37:21.397
No need to sell your car.

37:33.477 --> 37:33.997
Tastes great.

37:34.196 --> 37:35.317
Eat more vegetables.

37:37.437 --> 37:38.236
What soup is this?

37:38.917 --> 37:39.437
Chicken soup.

37:40.317 --> 37:40.997
So nourishing?

37:41.156 --> 37:41.596
Right.

37:53.196 --> 37:54.196
Since he found out

37:54.236 --> 37:55.716
you sold your car,

37:56.156 --> 37:57.357
could he's discovered

37:57.357 --> 37:58.317
you lied to him?

38:03.957 --> 38:04.877
Probably not.

38:08.036 --> 38:09.957
Zhou Zeyuan is terrifying.

38:10.397 --> 38:11.437
But why did he

38:11.437 --> 38:12.676
suddenly get caught?

38:14.556 --> 38:16.317
That's what puzzles me too.

38:16.917 --> 38:18.036
I feel like

38:19.076 --> 38:20.236
someone's helping me,

38:22.917 --> 38:24.116
but I don't know who.

38:33.357 --> 38:34.076
Never mind.

38:34.317 --> 38:34.997
Forget it.

38:35.437 --> 38:35.957
Anyway,

38:35.957 --> 38:37.036
it's resolved now.

38:37.156 --> 38:38.397
You should stop overthinking.

38:38.716 --> 38:39.757
Maybe you're just lucky,

38:39.917 --> 38:41.116
avoiding the dangers, right?

38:42.317 --> 38:42.917
But

38:43.236 --> 38:44.676
I still want to advise you.

38:45.236 --> 38:47.397
You can't keep hiding forever.

38:47.716 --> 38:49.357
Find a proper chance

38:49.516 --> 38:50.797
to explain to the Shen family.

38:51.317 --> 38:52.716
Your husband really loves you.

38:52.917 --> 38:53.997
Talk it through with him,

38:54.036 --> 38:55.196
and he'll forgive you.

38:55.477 --> 38:56.716
I do want to tell him.

38:59.757 --> 39:01.397
Just haven't found the right moment.

39:03.716 --> 39:04.076
Alright.

39:05.156 --> 39:06.397
That's good.

39:07.156 --> 39:08.716
I've been worried sick

39:08.716 --> 39:09.516
about this thing.

39:18.877 --> 39:19.636
It's ready.

39:21.236 --> 39:21.676
Eat up.

39:31.437 --> 39:32.076
Yu Yiming!

39:33.596 --> 39:34.397
Just off work?

39:34.636 --> 39:35.196
Had eaten?

39:35.596 --> 39:36.464
Yes, at the canteen.

39:36.957 --> 39:37.837
Xu Yan and I are here.

39:37.997 --> 39:38.997
Join us for more?

39:39.397 --> 39:40.357
The food here's good.

39:40.516 --> 39:41.797
- Come on.
- Okay.

39:41.797 --> 39:42.672
Just sit for a while.

39:43.116 --> 39:43.437
Come.

39:43.957 --> 39:44.277
Come.

39:44.477 --> 39:45.596
Try the lamb.

39:45.917 --> 39:46.317
Thanks.

39:47.116 --> 39:47.596
Off work?

39:49.837 --> 39:50.236
Here.

39:51.676 --> 39:52.076
Alright.

39:52.317 --> 39:52.757
Enough.

39:53.877 --> 39:54.277
Xu Yan.

39:55.236 --> 39:55.877
Yesterday, I saw

39:55.877 --> 39:56.997
the financial news.

39:57.116 --> 39:57.676
Honestly,

39:57.712 --> 39:58.877
you look great on camera.

39:59.196 --> 40:00.156
Stop teasing me.

40:00.317 --> 40:00.877
Just eat.

40:01.397 --> 40:02.036
I'm serious.

40:02.716 --> 40:03.036
Here.

40:03.357 --> 40:03.716
Try it.

40:03.716 --> 40:04.357
It's enough.

40:05.757 --> 40:06.437
Congratulations.

40:06.877 --> 40:08.156
You finally achieved your dream.

40:08.917 --> 40:09.397
Thank you.

40:10.196 --> 40:11.437
Sign an autograph for me later.

40:12.636 --> 40:13.397
When you're famous,

40:13.516 --> 40:14.997
I can show off

40:14.997 --> 40:15.797
to my coworkers.

40:16.156 --> 40:17.437
Don't overdo it, Yu Yiming.

40:19.716 --> 40:21.556
Not overdoing.

40:22.156 --> 40:22.716
Well,

40:23.357 --> 40:24.837
my coworkers

40:25.477 --> 40:27.236
all love watching that news

40:27.877 --> 40:28.596
and Family Feast.

40:29.196 --> 40:30.076
Since they learned

40:30.156 --> 40:31.757
we were high-school classmates,

40:32.156 --> 40:33.837
they talk about you all the time.

40:34.277 --> 40:34.757
Well,

40:35.116 --> 40:36.156
give me

40:36.196 --> 40:36.797
your autograph,

40:36.877 --> 40:37.477
okay?

40:38.317 --> 40:38.797
Qiao Lin.

40:40.357 --> 40:41.877
Isn't he tutoring you?

40:42.236 --> 40:42.997
How's it going?

40:43.236 --> 40:44.116
Excellent, of course.

40:44.156 --> 40:44.877
Just of average.

40:52.757 --> 40:53.357
Forget it.

40:53.797 --> 40:54.357
We finally

40:54.357 --> 40:54.917
reunite today.

40:55.076 --> 40:55.837
This meal's on me.

40:56.076 --> 40:56.556
My treat.

40:57.397 --> 40:58.036
Your treat?

40:59.357 --> 40:59.997
Waiter!

41:00.076 --> 41:01.277
30 more plates of lamb!

41:04.236 --> 41:04.837
You...

41:05.997 --> 41:06.997
Haven't seen Wolverine?

41:14.156 --> 41:15.196
The food was good today.

41:16.556 --> 41:16.997
Qiao Lin.

41:17.196 --> 41:17.596
What?

41:17.997 --> 41:18.957
What time to start?

41:19.277 --> 41:19.957
Starting what?

41:20.636 --> 41:21.277
The tutoring.

41:21.997 --> 41:23.277
After all that lamb?

41:24.036 --> 41:25.076
What's wrong with you?

41:25.357 --> 41:26.757
Overheated. Eaten too much lambs.

41:29.556 --> 41:30.236
Overheated?

41:31.636 --> 41:33.317
30 plates will do that.

42:33.036 --> 42:33.757
Are you busy?

42:40.116 --> 42:40.556
What's up?

42:45.877 --> 42:46.957
A friend

42:49.277 --> 42:50.477
just called me.

42:54.877 --> 42:56.076
She said before marriage,

42:56.076 --> 42:57.837
she hid something from her husband.

43:03.036 --> 43:04.596
Now she wants to confess.

43:09.116 --> 43:10.437
Why did she hide it?

43:16.196 --> 43:18.596
Afraid to ruin their relationship.

43:22.076 --> 43:22.957
And afraid

43:27.556 --> 43:29.156
he wouldn't have married her.

43:30.757 --> 43:32.877
How's their relationship now?

43:35.957 --> 43:36.437
Great.

43:39.596 --> 43:40.317
That's easy then.

43:41.076 --> 43:43.076
Then keep it hidden.

43:46.917 --> 43:48.277
Keep it hidden?

44:00.116 --> 44:01.437
- But I think...
- No buts.

44:05.196 --> 44:05.636
Listen.

44:14.596 --> 44:16.116
Tell your friend.

44:16.877 --> 44:18.357
Confession

44:19.156 --> 44:20.156
is like a thorn

44:20.236 --> 44:21.516
in marriage.

44:23.676 --> 44:24.716
Principles

44:24.757 --> 44:25.917
are not needed in marriage,

44:27.236 --> 44:27.837
right?

44:30.236 --> 44:33.116
Principles are just packaging.

44:33.196 --> 44:34.116
Empty words.

44:34.997 --> 44:35.997
In the end,

44:36.116 --> 44:37.516
a happy ending

44:38.116 --> 44:39.236
is what truly matters.

44:39.877 --> 44:40.397
Right?

44:45.116 --> 44:46.837
Stop worrying about others' problems.

44:46.837 --> 44:47.556
Okay?

44:48.076 --> 44:48.917
Think about me.

44:51.076 --> 44:51.556
Look.

44:54.556 --> 44:55.957
Yuanhang Fund.

44:56.596 --> 44:57.957
Jiang Liang and Jiang Yun

44:58.516 --> 45:00.076
(Yuanhang Fund)
will return to China next week.

45:00.917 --> 45:02.036
I've invited them

45:02.196 --> 45:03.596
to Jinda Group's reception.

45:06.716 --> 45:08.516
You need to help me prepare in advance

45:10.516 --> 45:11.397
to impress

45:11.504 --> 45:12.236
(Jiang Yun, Chairwoman)

45:12.236 --> 45:13.477
Jiang Yun.

45:20.116 --> 45:21.116
Look at her profile.

45:22.757 --> 45:24.596
Thirty-five years old.

45:25.236 --> 45:27.076
Calm,

45:27.716 --> 45:30.116
decisive.

45:43.952 --> 45:45.968
(Mr. Huang's calling)

45:47.076 --> 45:47.556
Hello?

45:48.116 --> 45:49.716
The New District project isn't getting

45:49.716 --> 45:50.957
your father's support now.

45:51.076 --> 45:51.877
We must find

45:51.957 --> 45:54.317
a fund company as backup.

45:54.957 --> 45:56.076
Jiang Liang and Jiang Yun

45:56.196 --> 45:57.596
are both back.

45:57.917 --> 45:59.636
Perfect chance

45:59.676 --> 46:00.556
to meet them.

46:01.036 --> 46:01.636
However,

46:01.757 --> 46:03.676
they're famously tough.

46:04.397 --> 46:04.957
Jiang Yun

46:05.676 --> 46:06.516
is calm,

46:06.716 --> 46:07.997
decisive in actions,

46:08.397 --> 46:10.236
and has a bad temper.

46:10.797 --> 46:11.917
(Jiang Yun, Chairwoman)
Known as

46:11.957 --> 46:13.277
the "Black Rose" of investing.

46:13.997 --> 46:14.676
Jiang Liang.

46:15.317 --> 46:17.877
Don't be fooled by the playboy look.

46:18.277 --> 46:19.757
He's meticulous-minded,

46:19.957 --> 46:21.397
(Jiang Liang, Deputy Manager)
a numbers genius.

46:21.676 --> 46:23.516
Key to Yuanhang Fund's finance.

46:23.997 --> 46:26.156
Rumor says he has a photographic memory.

46:27.156 --> 46:28.716
This is all I can help you.

46:29.397 --> 46:30.757
The rest is up to you.

46:31.116 --> 46:32.076
Thank you, Mr. Huang.

